ition\n|-\n| 1. || 5 September 2009 || [[Hampden Park]], [[Glasgow]] || {{fb|MKD}} || <center> 1\u20130</center> || <center>2\u20130</center> || [[2010 FIFA World Cup qualification \u2013 UEFA Group 9|2010 World Cup qualifier]]\n|-\n| 2. || 3 March 2010 || Hampden Park, Glasgow || {{fb|CZE}} || <center>1\u20130</center> || <center>1\u20130</center> || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 3. || 19 November 2013 || [[Aker Stadion]], [[Molde]] || {{fb|NOR}} || <center>1\u20130</center> || <center>1\u20130</center> || Friendly\n|-\n| 4. || 5 March 2014 || [[National Stadium, Warsaw|National Stadium]], [[Warsaw]] || {{fb|POL}} || <center>1\u20130</center> || <center>1\u20130</center> || Friendly\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Hibernian'''\n*[[Scottish League Cup]]: [[2006\u201307 Scottish League Cup|2006\u201307]]<ref name=\"HibsLC07\" />\n\n'''Celtic'''\n*[[list of Scottish football champions|Scottish Premiership]] (9): [[2007\u201308 Scottish Premier League|2007\u201308]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/7412454.stm|title=Dundee United 0\u20131 Celtic|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|accessdate=5 April 2017}}</ref> [[2011\u201312 Scottish Premier League|2011\u201312]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/17570842|title=Kilmarnock 0\u20136 Celtic|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|accessdate=5 April 2017}}</ref> [[2012\u201313 Scottish Premier League|2012\u201313]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/22409613|title=Celtic 4\u20130 St Johnstone|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|accessdate=5 April 2017}}</ref> [[2013\u201314 Scottish Premiership|2013\u201314]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/26641424|title=Partick Thistle 1\u20135 Celtic|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|accessdate=5 April 2017}}</ref> [[2014\u201315 Scottish Premiership|2014\u201315]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/32664511|title=Celtic 5\u20130 Inverness CT|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|accessdate=5 April 2017}}</ref> [[2015\u201