elebrity on Twitter\n| {{nom|Finalist}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\" rowspan=\"3\"|[[O Music Awards]]\n|align=\"center\"| Must-Follow Artist on Twitter\n| {{nom}}\n|rowspan=\"3\"|\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| Best Male Solo Artist\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|align=\"center\"| Best Choreography\n|align=\"center\"| \"Abandoned\"\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|2012\n|align=\"center\"| Asia Model Awards\n|align=\"center\"| Popular Artist Award\n|align=\"center\"| Jay Park\n| {{won}}\n|<ref name=\"AMFA\" /><ref name=\"asiamodelawards1\" /><ref name=\"asiamodelawards2\" />\n|-\n| 2013\n|align=\"center\"| [[Shout! Awards]]\n|align=\"center\"| Flava Award\n|align=\"center\"| Jay Park & [[Mizz Nina]]\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n|2014\n|align=\"center\"| SBS MTV Best of the Best\n|align=\"center\"| Best Hip Hop Music Video\n|align=\"center\"| \"So Good\"\n|{{won}}\n|<ref name=sbsmtvbestofthebest>{{cite web|title=2014 MTV SBS Best of the Best|url=http://www.mtv.co.kr/mini/2014-best-of-the-best|publisher=SBS MTV}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official|www.jaypark.com}}\n<!--per [[WP:EL]], ONE official site is allowed.-->\n{{Commons category|Jay Park}}\n\n{{Jay Park}}\n{{2PM}}\n{{JYP Entertainment}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Park, Jay}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:2PM members]]\n[[Category:Jay Park]]\n[[Category:21st-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:American breakdancers]]\n[[Category:American chief executives]]\n[[Category:American choreographers]]\n[[Category:21st-century American composers]]\n[[Category:American contemporary R&B singers]]\n[[Category:American expatriates in South Korea]]\n[[Category:American hip hop record producers]]\n[[Category:American hip hop singers]]\n[[Category:American male actors of Korean descent]]\n[[Category:American male composers]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male rappers]]\n[[Category:American mass media owners]]\n[[Category:American media company fo